        <mxCell id="guardrails" value="Guardrails: canonical pk.yml is not auto-edited by workflow runs. Validation emits OK/WARN/FAILED only. Calibration and external tool results stay as separate artifacts. BLQ/M3-ready columns are fixture contracts, not formal likelihood estimation. SDTM-like and ADPC-like outputs are workflow fixtures, not submission-ready datasets." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FEF3C7;strokeColor=#D97706;fontSize=13;align=left;spacingLeft=14;fontStyle=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
